{"tid":1240431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一間支持香港警察既店舖","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T10:39:27.000Z","uid":215664,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"395858ad0ccb92e7c52d22f92e550239a61fe15e","tid":1240431,"uid":215664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"尋日同朋友去買鞋 傾返612果日既野<br />\n跟住俾個中年老細聽到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老細：話我地廢青 話我地得閒冇嘢做出去搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住佢話佢自己個仔係香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話為佢個仔感到驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢嘈左幾句 比佢問候母親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢間鋪比搞搞震嘅廢青黎 比佢趕左我地走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以去多啲幫襯支持返香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />討論下佢個仔有幾威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚發夢夢到佢個地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田瀝源邨福海樓 12號鋪 南發皮具鞋業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：用朋友account <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家可以提供更加多支持香港警察嘅店舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}